race.comment: MORDECAI (3) ran a strong race last time out over 2000m at this track, finishing fourth and beaten 2 lengths. Suitably placed so anticipating a big run against this line-up. CASH ARTIST (5) raced on the speed from the outset last start and finished second, beaten 0.8 lengths, over 2000m here. Placed to advantage so expect a big run. BIKER (2) comes back in class after finishing 12 lengths away in ninth over 2406m at Eagle Farm three weeks ago when he was always well back. This is much easier and can play a big role in the finish. FLYBALL (7) has been thereabouts of late and may earn some minor money.
